Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.13,0:00:20.30,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It hasn't been nearly long enough
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.94,0:00:23.69,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But I seem to be doing alright
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.26,0:00:31.58,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I was today; I made my meals~~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.61,0:00:36.49,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Some days I can't be sure
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:38.27,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That I'm out of my curse
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.48,0:00:40.60,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That I can't go back again~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.53,0:00:48.74,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I secretly hope I won't~ if I~ try~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.69,0:01:09.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I see friendly faces from time to time~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.01,0:01:13.69,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Some days it's hard to even stand upright~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.03,0:01:15.77,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Some days are better
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.16,0:01:23.99,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I even go outside
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.05,0:01:58.10,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's true that time heals all wounds
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.12,0:02:02.08,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Maybe it works both ways
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.19,0:02:06.02,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,One fate for me and for the rest of us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.49,0:02:09.58,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Where consequence is a novel idea~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.07,0:02:14.33,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And it still feels like~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.13,0:02:18.44,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Another encore's a blink away~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.65,0:02:20.43,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,There's something better ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.94,0:02:22.42,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And it's waiting for me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:26.62,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Wait for me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.08,0:02:46.96,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Along the streets that saw me die~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.63,0:02:50.13,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The rain is dancing under the sun~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:53.95,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It washed away~ all the blood and the death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.24,0:02:57.04,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And all that's left is all the time that is mine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:03:00.47,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I can wait~ for peace to catch up with my head
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.38,0:03:04.67,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For the surprises up ahead~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:08.74,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For the decisions left to make
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:12.80,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For all the love left to give~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:16.58,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And I know it's been~ rough
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.74,0:03:18.35,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And I can't say enough
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:20.43,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And neither can I pretend
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.73,0:03:22.42,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That I understand
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:25.73,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But if you put your trust in me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:29.58,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'll show you how special your time can be
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:32.76,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And even if I can't know what it's like
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.97,0:03:34.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Because your life's not mine
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:36.66,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I can show you that I care
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:38.74,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For you I'm always there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:42.21,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You have someone to help you see things through
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.55,0:03:47.04,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,If you believe in me I'll be good to you too
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.65,0:04:07.93,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be lonely
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.69,0:04:11.41,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'll stay, I'll stay, with you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:16.07,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When I feel like I'm falling
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.87,0:04:19.54,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'll stay, I'll stay, with you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.92,0:04:24.37,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When the nightmares get to me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.96,0:04:27.68,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'll stay, I'll stay, with you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.06,0:04:32.89,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When I feel too tired to breathe~~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:36.66,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'll stay, I'll stay, with you~~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:41.24,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,'Cause in this time~line~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.79,0:04:45.35,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We've got a shot at a happy ending
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:50.47,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The rest can wait until tomorrow
